summary:
- **Stop Loss Trigger Event**: The CitiFirst MINI (ASX Code: SPFKOU) has been suspended due to the S&P500 eMINI Futures (Sep-2025) trading at or below the Stop Loss Level of **6,368.0000**.  
- **Temporary Trading Window**: A bid at the Cash Amount will be displayed from **2pm on 22 July 2025** until **4pm on 23 July 2025** for holders to sell their MINIs to Citi.  
- **Termination & Payment**: If not sold during the trading window, holders will receive the Stop Loss Amount within **10 Business Days**, and the MINIs will expire upon payment.  

No other material information identified.
